{"tid":1743502,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"沙駕考車4take","createTime":"2019-11-21T08:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T11:56:26.000Z","uid":32663,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"54f47ab6b03933bbb0a9a4cc60e98ab92bb71e03","tid":1743502,"uid":32663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:32:30.000Z","msg":"今日考3點，考車前練車，銀城線練亂到hi一聲<br />\n多死車、上下客小巴校巴私家車、唔睇燈既廢老<br />\n<br />\n上次考銀城衰廢老紅燈過馬路，心諗唔通今次又出事<br />\n係房仔等叫名已經驚到震，勁驚又係考銀城<br />\n<br />\n點知遇著個好人考官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n考多石線，全程冇mark任何野冇比壓力<br />\n成條多石都係得同學仔學車，冇巴士貨車<br />\n<br />\n考車真係撞手神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec8b3542fb5148238cddfb501bf0e9c5be0a0d3","tid":1743502,"uid":71058,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:33:40.000Z","msg":"銀城不嬲最難, 好多死車"},{"pid":"cb558b0807c88649751fbdd41f289eb30e4724bf","tid":1743502,"uid":33973,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:34:44.000Z","msg":"銀城算易<br />\n多石＜銀城＜河畔"},{"pid":"e463fee7f89c461c6e1f8d6de4777acae9c3785d","tid":1743502,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:35:19.000Z","msg":"棍van 1 take<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df459f8e143b52c30bae61f082e7d2167351fd1","tid":1743502,"uid":32663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e463fee7f89c461c6e1f8d6de4777acae9c3785d","tid":1743502,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:35:19.000Z","msg":"棍van 1 take<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:35:39.000Z","msg":"威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38831302002044867abcb89d276dd5a9add4d460","tid":1743502,"uid":32663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb558b0807c88649751fbdd41f289eb30e4724bf","tid":1743502,"uid":33973,"l